title: 3K Subs! Update Message
description:
Hello there friends, I have been quite slow to post videos as of late so I decided it was about time for an update. Plus I reached 3K subs last week!!!!

follow me on twitter @andrealynnlewis
email me at andreawiththebangs@gmail.com
follow my vintage Instagram @fringevintagefinds
